{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0400e1d7eb","title":"李富春与成都“工人造反兵团”谈关于揪斗李井泉的问题","origin":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"75d185e3f1","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":30,"articleId":"0400e1d7eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"25e2abfb25","name":"李富春","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9c4175f9ee","name":"李富春"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"af35ec76a1","type":"title","text":"李富春与成都“工人造反兵团”谈关于揪斗李井泉的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"615f5678d1","type":"authors","text":"李富春","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"601826901a","type":"subtitle","text":"(1967年7月30日16:50 在人大会堂我院革委会成立大会主席台上)","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"f68e6f4c19","type":"paragraph","text":"问：我们(兵团)想请示一下关于揪斗李井泉的问题。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"6f2fc295af","type":"paragraph","text":"李：(很生气，语气极重)成都揪斗李井泉，总理根本不知道，总理还在跟他们要人。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"0b8209ec93","type":"paragraph","text":"问：既然不是总理同意的，我们就得给成都去电话辟谣。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"6298d129c1","type":"paragraph","text":"李：完全可以。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"e20a761a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"周恩来联络员温伯华与成都“工人造反兵团”的谈话：","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"38bb078391","type":"paragraph","text":"问：关于“红成”揪斗李井泉问题是怎么样的？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"},{"id":"b8ea03d018","type":"paragraph","text":"温：“红成”先把李井泉非法的弄去，然后给总理打了个电话去，总理不同意这种做法，后来总理说：“既然你们抓去了，开完会，立即送回来。”","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb"}],"page":{"id":"d39d4c44ef","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0400e1d7eb","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}